:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:46:52.000Z","msg":"蒼天已死。黃天當立。<br />\n遲d四川到舊殞石似&quot;包子&quot;. 又可能吹噓習包子天命所歸。應當封王"},{"pid":"819e2c29c64c9261cf60a3cafa58fe97534b059c","tid":439322,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:48:32.000Z","msg":"風水佬呃你十年八載... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e2fe7a3f338d7b433f52a00baab7f6f3c46b59","tid":439322,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"搞清楚，官方並無此說法，不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到好似習大大授意咁。"}]}